'''加州大麻控制局'''（{{lang-en|Bureau of Cannabis Control}}），原名'''加州医用大麻管制局'''（{{lang|en|Bureau of Medical Marijuana Regulation}}）<ref>{{citation|title=Update: Changes for New Medical Cannabis Regulation Bureau|date=August 3, 2016|work=official blog|publisher=State of California Department of Consumer Affairs|url=https://thedcapage.wordpress.com/2016/08/03/update-changes-for-new-medical-cannabis-regulation-bureau/|accessdate=2021-02-10|archive-date=2017-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517004957/https://thedcapage.wordpress.com/2016/08/03/update-changes-for-new-medical-cannabis-regulation-bureau/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citation|title=AN ANALYSIS OF CALIFORNIA'S MEDICAL MARIJUANA REGULATION & SAFETY ACT|publisher=California Police Chiefs Association|url=http://www.californiapolicechiefs.org/assets/Marijuana/Medical%2520Marijuana%2520Package_Summary%2520for%2520Chiefs.pdf|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414184644/http://www.californiapolicechiefs.org/assets/Marijuana/Medical%20Marijuana%20Package_Summary%20for%20Chiefs.pdf|archivedate=2016-04-14}}</ref>，是美国[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]消费事务部（{{lang|en|Department of Consumer Affairs}}）下属的一个机构，负责根据《医用大麻管制法》（{{lang|en|''Medical Cannabis Regulation and Safety Act''}}）和《成人大麻使用法》（{{lang|en|''Adult Use of Marijuana Act''}}）管理[[医用大麻|医用大麻]]（{{lang|en|MMJ}}）的开发、销售和使用。自2018年1月1日起，该机构也开始负责非医用大麻市场相关的法律法规。该机构的首任领导是洛瑞·阿贾克斯（{{lang|en|Lori Ajax}}）于2017年2月上任，他被多个媒体戏称为“加州大麻沙皇”。<ref>{{citation|title=California Marijuana Tax and Tracking Systems Behind Schedule: Lawmaker|date=February 14, 2017|author=Rory Carroll|publisher=Reuters|via=US News|url=https://www.usnews.com/news/us/articles/2017-02-14/california-marijuana-tax-and-tracking-systems-behind-schedule-lawmaker}}</ref>

